This is a family staple! My kids are picky, and they love it! I make it basically verbatim (for 15 years), and think the fresh herbs and lemon are key. I squeeze extra lemon at the table. It's best with fresh corn, but any corn will do in a pinch. And for picky eaters, this is a great, quick and easy meal.

