Rating: 3
This recipe is easy and delicious. I've only had the recipe for 2 weeks and have already made it twice. The second time I made it with brown rice to add fiber. It was good, but better with the white rice. The newer canned chicken broths with garlic, herbs, etc. adds additional flavor. We don't make many seafood dishes at home...this one is a keeper.

Rating: 3
